ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent Ticagrelor therapy used to reduce stroke mortality and morbidity.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Medication.
